# UDBZ - UDIF bzip2-compressed image (Mac OS X 10.4+ only)
# ULFO - UDIF lzfse-compressed image (OS X 10.11+ only)
# ULMO - UDIF lzma-compressed image (macOS 10.15+ only)
# Volume format (see hdiutil create -help)

